<英文法規名稱>Regulations of Investment Ceilings and Guidelines Governing Financial Holding Company’s Venture Capital Subsidiaries Investing in Non-financial Enterprises Not Listed on Taiwan Stock Exchange or Taipei Exchange</英文法規名稱>
